'''Grigmin's Traveling Airshow''' was an airshow put on by [[Grigmin]] in the years shortly before the [[Battle of Yavin/Legends|Battle of Yavin]]. [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] and [[Chewbacca/Legends|Chewbacca]] worked as mechanics for the airshow briefly.

